<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Unrecognized on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/unrecognized/</link><description>Recent content in Unrecognized on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/unrecognized/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] TypeScript TS1435 — Unknown Keyword or Identifier</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts1435/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts1435/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="ts1435--unknown-keyword-or-identifier"&gt;TS1435 — Unknown keyword or identifier&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TS1435 occurs when TypeScript encounters an identifier that it doesn&amp;rsquo;t recognize as a valid keyword or identifier in the current context. This often means a typo in a keyword, using a future/reserved word, or an unrecognized syntax.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Typo in a keyword
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;pritn&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS1435: &amp;#39;pritn&amp;#39; is not recognized (typo of &amp;#39;print&amp;#39;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Using a keyword from another language
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;greet&lt;/span&gt;()&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS1435: &amp;#39;def&amp;#39; is not a TypeScript keyword (Python syntax)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Unrecognized decorator or modifier
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;@sealed&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS1435 if decorator not recognized or not enabled
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;MyClass&lt;/span&gt; {}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: Misspelled type annotation keyword
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;numberr&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS1435: &amp;#39;numberr&amp;#39; is not a valid type
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="solutions"&gt;Solutions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-correct-keyword-typos"&gt;Fix 1: Correct keyword typos&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;pritn&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-valid-typescript-keywords"&gt;Fix 2: Use valid TypeScript keywords&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong — Python syntax
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;greet&lt;/span&gt;()&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct — TypeScript function
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;greet&lt;/span&gt;()&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; {}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-enable-decorator-support-if-needed"&gt;Fix 3: Enable decorator support if needed&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// tsconfig.json
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;{
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;#34;compilerOptions&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;#34;experimentalDecorators&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;#34;emitDecoratorMetadata&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-fix-type-annotation-typos"&gt;Fix 4: Fix type annotation typos&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;numberr&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Using a non-existent type
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Arrray&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; []; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS1435: &amp;#39;Arrray&amp;#39; not recognized
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fix:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Array&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [];
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Wrong loop syntax from another language
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;range&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;) { &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS1435: not valid TypeScript
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fix:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;++&lt;/span&gt;) {}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts1434/"&gt;TS1434: Unexpected keyword or identifier&lt;/a&gt; — keyword in wrong position.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2304/"&gt;TS2304: Cannot find name&lt;/a&gt; — identifier not in scope.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts1128/"&gt;TS1128: Declaration or statement expected&lt;/a&gt; — broader parse error.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>